1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,169
Deep in the forests of Sleepywood... a shaman named Chrishrama performs a ritual he has carried out many times before.

2
00:00:10,169 --> 00:00:20,164
He presses glowing charms onto the ancient Shaman Rocks — a ward against the evil that seeps from the earth below.

3
00:00:20,164 --> 00:00:26,476
The purple energy rising through the cracks is faint... but it is growing.

4
00:00:26,476 --> 00:00:28,755
Chrishrama does not panic.

5
00:00:28,755 --> 00:00:34,454
He has lived beside this darkness long enough to know its rhythm.

6
00:00:34,454 --> 00:00:37,873
But tonight... something feels different.
